content: Hey, https://github.com/rust-lang/rust-clippy/pull/6966 is a pretty big PR and I can't seem to find time to review it, does anyone else want to take over?
I would like to try my hands on some reviews, so I would take it if that's okay. I could also hand it over for a final review afterwards :upside_down:
@xFrednet thank you! and yeah i'll keep an eye out
it's a big PR, try to be thorough :)
Thank you for giving me the opportunity, I'll do my best! I've already started running lintcheck and reading into the code :upside_down:
@xFrednet I'm concerned that if you do not turn yourself upright soon, you will suffer from too much blood pressure in your brain.
:smile: ¿ʇɥƃᴉɹ ɹǝʇʇǝq ǝq plnoɥs sᴉɥʇ ¡ʎɹɹos sdn ˙˙˙ɯɥn ˙˙˙ɥɥO
I actually use the upside down smiley that much that I don't know the text form of the normal one ^^
Did you flip your icon or am I upside down now?
You're up right, from my perspective :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes:

Back to the topic of the PR. I've started to review it but it takes some time as expected. I hope to finish it tomorrow, I would ping you in the review @Manish Goregaokar to look over my questions/suggestions if that's okay with you? :upside_down:
